<h2>Help & FAQ</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>How do I set my location?</strong><br />Use the 📍 button on your dashboard or drawer nav.</li>
  <li><strong>How do I join a community?</strong><br />Go to Discover → Communities and click “Join”.</li>
  <li><strong>Who sees my location?</strong><br />Only your matched friends, and only if you've enabled public location sharing.</li>
</ul>